{"tid":1563202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831 事實擺在眼前 根本無fake news","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T10:13:00.000Z","uid":125389,"like":410,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa4ddf436d75d40dabf2c9949e6a176851f032c","tid":1563202,"uid":125389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:19:35.000Z","msg":"其實作為一個醫護人員<br />\n我可以好肯定咁話俾大家聽<br />\n當時第一個報出黎既人數無可能錯<br />\n<br />\n救護主任本身就有訓練點去manage人數<br />\n之前咁多巴士事故 你有無見佢地點錯數？<br />\n今次只係十個傷者 仲要有6個係紅色<br />\n一個醫護人員係果個環境 一定無可能重覆點紅色人數<br />\n因為佢地既傷同徵狀都完全唔同<br />\n你話唔見其他無咁嚴重都唔合理 何況係紅色case<br />\n<br />\n老老實實 果三個人好明顯俾黑警留左係太子<br />\n淨低既果7個就送去荔枝角 再交俾救護送醫院<br />\n消防高層深藍一家親 㩒住D細既再講大話<br />\n話自己只係收到7個傷者 佢咁講的確無錯<br />\n另一邊黑警封站兩個幾鐘 就係call上頭處理三個死者<br />\n因為俾人落去就會發現屍體 而港鐵知情受脅唔公開cctv<br />\n<br />\n大家唔洗再fact check 根本呢三個人死係事實<br />\n消防 港鐵 黑警 全部高層深藍 低級救護消防滅晒聲"},{"pid":"045f5ccf316e2b35ced4c8fa4d78e71066810d92","tid":1563202,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:20:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"67c70fb5c0e376246d1131f905007335b91ff3fb","tid":1563202,"uid":125389,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\n大家最應該對黑警宣傳<br />\n毛EE有餓底係黑警群中<br />